Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.45,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.53,0:00:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.21,0:00:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.56,0:00:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.54,0:01:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.61,0:01:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.62,0:01:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.82,0:01:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,幫我拿一下鹽巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,妳沒聽到嗎,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你擅自去音無家\N說她想辭掉管理員的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.34,0:02:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那麼做哪裡不對了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經曠職一個禮拜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.97,0:02:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒被炒魷魚才奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,不需要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.79,0:02:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我反而很感謝妳這幾年來\N為我們家這麼忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.39,0:02:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也請了新的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是暫時代理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼請了新的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不可能乖乖接受才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為除了我之外\N絕對沒人可以勝任這個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.91,0:02:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#91響子愕然!\N朱美和五代有著意外的關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.12,0:02:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,你們不要太過份好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我怎麼有時間\N去接管理員呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.76,0:03:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你和小津江徹底分手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳突然問這個幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有分手的話\N去接幾次都沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用,沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你乾脆跟小津江在一起好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也名正言順的\N接收了管理員的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會說風涼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,請不要在這裡開宴會!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.56,0:03:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(時鐘坡)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.50,0:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?\N不好意思回去一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.28,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,五代變成代理管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.92,0:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在跩得要命\N居然禁止我們在走廊喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛,這個男人實在太霸道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼都在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好意思回來見我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我們添了那麼多麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,不要這樣說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.48,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一直責怪她,多可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.55,0:04:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她為了道歉\N也已經說要請客了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.25,0:04:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.66,0:04:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.29,0:04:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會就這樣辭掉\N管理員的工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.70,0:04:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有這種打算,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.13,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為五代和小津江糾纏不清嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能還要花上個一百年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳悶不吭聲逃掉的這段時間\N說不定他們更加親密了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的這樣的話,我也無話可說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.55,0:05:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那我來勾引五代好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,妳聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是個令人玩味的發言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.57,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近光只是有人陪著睡\N感覺有點慾求不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟他上床嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的會做哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的這樣的話,我也無話可說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒意見啊\N那我就去勾引他了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請便,隨妳高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,350圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-啊,找錢\N-不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.87,0:06:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候去一趟一刻館\N跟新的管理員打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就打算這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新來的管理員雖然很可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我回去工作,還有得等呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.33,0:06:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是挺意外的\N想不到朱美居然對五代有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,我是在開玩笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.53,0:06:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從妳嘴巴講出來\N聽起來不像開玩笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.07,0:06:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.31,0:06:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不稍微嚇嚇她的話\N以她那種個性會賭氣不回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人真麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想做就儘管去做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.15,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是那麼\N經不起誘惑的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.46,0:06:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意志薄弱,膽小懦弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼五代在打掃呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,廁所的鎖壞掉了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦\N不要一直叫我管理員啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,原來新的管理員是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,電話響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,真是忙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我窮緊張一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,朱美跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說要去約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.26,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會?跟誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是五代哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定她白天說的是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,朱美是個會假戲真做的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確蠻有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是五代,請問是哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?朱美?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在附近,你猜我在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喝醉了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著錢,到我跟你說的地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢?妳別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,我死了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.55,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哭嗎?\N喂,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭,我已經夠忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.89,0:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,在這裡轉彎\N第二棟大樓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賓館…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.77,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有搞錯吧\N可是朱美怎麼會在這裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是302號房的客人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,對啊,我是她的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一位小姐等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.32,0:09:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,電梯在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.24,0:09:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道朱美在邀我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,開門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,門沒鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,醒醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳醒醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,醒醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.06,0:10:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱…朱美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會跑來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,是妳叫我來的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.68,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你來的?我叫你來幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.78,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想問妳呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉,不小心喝太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人趁我睡著\N偷偷溜走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,喝得好過癮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.64,0:11:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼好猶豫的\N跟收入穩定的男人結婚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,不然妳會吃苦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,如果沒有我陪在身邊\N五代他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.68,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種沒出息的人\N誰跟在他身邊都沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦\N你拖拖拉拉的在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不好啦,會被人家看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會在這種地方碰見熟人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.20,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,妳認識他們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.49,0:13:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?很清爽的早晨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能清爽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼啊,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.17,0:13:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是總算能跟小津江\N斷得一乾二淨了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十之八九被小津江甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,你們還真的分得了手耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的囉,因為從賓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.42,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.76,0:13:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算被知道也沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是可以到處張揚的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在緊張什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有緊張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個之間\N發生了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?怎麼可能會有什麼事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.07,0:13:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,要是有的話\N我還會對他另眼相看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,你要感謝我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的關係\N你們才能徹底地做個了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.22,0:14:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這種方式分手,真的好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我是五代,我要找小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,小津江嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.03,0:14:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在聽嗎?\N關於昨晚的事,還有很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟妳見個面談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,誰打來的電話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,是打錯電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟她重修舊好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡站多久了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美把事情都告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要管她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.31,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算誤會說清楚了\N你還是得跟她再提分手的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算分手\N我也要成為美麗的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.58,0:15:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直活在她的心裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.02,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在打這種如意算盤吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有,才沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-別傻了\N-別傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.46,0:15:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.67,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子\N一刻館的人等妳很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是一之瀨太太啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是五代,很抱歉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我沒有這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?分手了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,分得一乾二淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也差不多可以回來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經如妳所願了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼說\N我沒有這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.52,0:16:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…他向小津江求婚了,不是嗎\N怎麼可以這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.59,0:16:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那是一場誤會\N單純的誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,他都沒有跟我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳不肯聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.34,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說,由五代來當管理員\N粗心大意的實在很靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我叫五代\N明天來接妳回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我自己可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己…可以回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,總算得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳會把狗一起帶走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能把牠放在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.16,0:17:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N你把我的事向小津江說了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.60,0:17:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員明天就會回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說\N管理員已經知道真相了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.78,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟小津江是怎麼分手的\N千萬不可以再提起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.35,0:17:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,畢竟我們兩個\N從賓館出來是不爭的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.52,0:17:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賓…賓館?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我實在太羨慕你了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是一起出來而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但總要先進去才能出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.23,0:18:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來,我醒來的時候\N你還趴在我身上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.67,0:18:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是清白的話\N就直直地看著我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然恩將仇報…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.98,0:18:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是表示一點謝意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賓館的費用快點還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,上賓館居然叫女人付錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定上床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.43,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.20,0:18:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天管理員就要回來了\N你怎麼還幹這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們不相信我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要當真啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.21,0:18:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你根本沒有那種膽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.24,0:18:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳也不要太捉弄人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.28,0:19:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戲弄五代實在太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.12,0:19:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,提前慶祝管理員復職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.61,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦\N今天就要被炒魷魚了對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.47,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的平交道又塞車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我在這裡下就可以了\N已經很近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,這樣或許比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去旅行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.76,0:20:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微陪我聊聊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.39,0:21:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.13,0:21:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來五代他有喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.70,0:21:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.40,0:21:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代果然把我的事告訴她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.91,0:21:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼說才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,不用再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.58,0:21:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然受到一點打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.52,0:21:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,也因為這樣下定了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.29,0:21:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳轉告五代\N說我不會再跟他見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.12,0:22:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.23,0:22:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.13,0:22:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為五代很體貼\N我以為他會好好珍惜我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.24,0:22:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我萬萬沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.58,0:22:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然會跟那種人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.58,0:22:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好傻哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.72,0:22:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的''那種人''是指誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.39,0:23:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻館的朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.23,0:23:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.16,0:23:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我親眼看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.57,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人從賓館走出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.51,0:23:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員好慢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.15,0:23:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能去買東西了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的會回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息、卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.34,0:23:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩女人、拈花惹草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.58,0:23:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低級的爛男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\N兩人還是重新和好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.41,0:24:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N那個令人跌破眼鏡的小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.55,0:24:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.75,0:24:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.32,0:24:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『小津江結婚!\N五代的愛直到永遠?』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.72,0:24:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.00,0:24:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.63,0:24:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.94,0:24:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.88,0:24:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.98,0:24:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.22,0:24:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.86,0:24:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.67,0:24:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.44,0:24:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.71,0:25:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.55,0:25:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.39,0:25:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.10,0:25:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.37,0:25:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.61,0:25:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
